data.description: Stunning view home perched atop the sought after Highland Estates neighborhood! Open and airy floorplan with 5 br/4.5 ba, over 5,000 SF. Situated on a .35 acre lot w/ views from almost every room! Enormous chef's kitchen including oversized island with sueded granite, commercial size fridge/freezer, gas range, top of the line cabinets. Dining room is the perfect spot to host your friends & family while enjoying the sunset. Kitchen & dining open up to the oversized living room w/ custom built-ins, full bath, laundry & office. Upstairs is the primary suite, 2 guest rooms & a guest bath. Spacious primary suite w/ full tiled shower, double vanity, soaker tub & walk in closet. Lower level w/ large rec room/playroom, guest room, guest suite & additional ½ bath. Basement w/ ample storage + large flex space w/potential to be a future in-law suite or workshop! Fully fenced backyard with sprinklers, mature landscaping, and fruit trees. Truly a gem!
